<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>OAgroCota — Gestão de Cotações para Consultores Agrícolas</title>
<meta name="description" content="Pare de perder tempo com planilhas. Gerencie cotações, propostas e a gestão financeira da safra — tudo no celular, em minutos.">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#000">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --black:#000;--d1:#070d07;--d2:#0b150b;
  --gbrand:#256626;--gmid:#2f8031;--glight:#3ea841;--gglow:#52c455;--gpale:#b5deb6;
  --gold:#e8961e;--gold2:#f5c540;
  --white:#fff;--ts:rgba(255,255,255,0.62);--tm:rgba(255,255,255,0.34);
}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
body{font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;background:#000;color:#fff;overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6;}
img{display:block;max-width:100%;}a{text-decoration:none;}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:300;height:70px;padding:0 48px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);}
.nav-logo img{height:52px;width:auto;}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:22px;}
.nav-link{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-size:.88rem;font-weight:500;transition:color .2s;}
.nav-link:hover{color:#fff;}
.nav-btn{background:var(--glight);color:#fff;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;
  font-size:.88rem;padding:11px 26px;border-radius:10px;border:none;cursor:pointer;
  box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(62,168,65,0.35);transition:background .2s,transform .15s,box-shadow .2s;}
.nav-btn:hover{background:var(--gglow);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(62,168,65,0.5);}

/* HERO */
.hero{min-height:100vh;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse 95% 65% at 50% 38%,rgba(37,102,38,0.22) 0%,transparent 62%),
             linear-gradient(175deg,#010801 0%,#091209 50%,#000 100%);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  padding:96px 24px 52px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:240px;
  background:linear-gradient(transparent,#000);pointer-events:none;}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  background:rgba(82,196,85,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(82,196,85,0.24);
  color:var(--gpale);font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.13em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:7px 20px;border-radius:50px;margin-bottom:36px;}
.pdot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gglow);animation:blink 2.2s ease infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:.3;transform:scale(1.5)}}
.hero h1{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-weight:400;
  font-size:clamp(2.6rem,7.5vw,5.2rem);color:#fff;max-width:880px;margin:0 auto 24px;
  letter-spacing:-.01em;line-height:1.07;}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gglow);}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,2.2vw,1.18rem);color:var(--ts);
  max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 52px;line-height:1.76;}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:76px;}
.btn-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbrand),var(--glight));color:#fff;
  font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;
  padding:18px 44px;border-radius:13px;border:none;cursor:pointer;
  box-shadow:0 4px 32px rgba(62,168,65,0.42);transition:all .25s;}
.btn-hero:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 48px rgba(82,196,85,0.55);}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);
  font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:500;font-size:1rem;
  padding:18px 34px;border-radius:13px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
  transition:all .2s;cursor:pointer;}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.36);color:#fff;}
.phones-hero{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;gap:26px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
.ph-center img{width:220px;filter:drop-shadow(0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.95)) drop-shadow(0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.08));}
.ph-side{opacity:.6;}
.ph-side.l{transform:rotate(-8deg) translateY(36px);}
.ph-side.r{transform:rotate(8deg) translateY(36px);}
.ph-side img{width:168px;filter:drop-shadow(0 28px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.9));}

/* SECTIONS */
.sec{padding:112px 24px;}
.wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
.label{font-size:.71rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gglow);margin-bottom:16px;}
.h2{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-weight:400;
  font-size:clamp(2.1rem,4.8vw,3.4rem);letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#fff;line-height:1.09;}
.h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gglow);}
.h2 .g{color:var(--gold);}
.body-txt{font-size:1.04rem;color:var(--ts);line-height:1.76;}

/* DOR */
.dor-sec{background:var(--d1);}
.dor-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:center;align-content:center;}
.dor-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;margin-top:40px;}
.dor-card{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start;padding:22px 24px;border-radius:16px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.025);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.052);
  border-left:3px solid #b71c1c;transition:background .2s,transform .2s;}
.dor-card:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);transform:translateX(4px);}
.dor-ico{font-size:1.55rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
.dor-card h4{font-weight:700;font-size:.94rem;color:#ef9a9a;margin-bottom:5px;}
.dor-card p{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);line-height:1.62;}
/* Illustration panel */
.dor-visual{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;align-self:center;}
.dor-visual img{
  width:100%;max-width:520px;
  border-radius:20px;
  box-shadow:0 24px 72px rgba(0,0,0,0.85),0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  display:block;
}

/* FEATURES */
.feat-sec{background:#000;}
.feat-intro{text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 72px;}
.feat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:22px;}
.fc{background:var(--d2);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.062);border-radius:24px;
  overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s,border-color .3s,box-shadow .3s;}
.fc:hover{transform:translateY(-10px);border-color:rgba(82,196,85,0.28);
  box-shadow:0 28px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.62);}
.fc-phone{width:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(160deg,#0c180c,#0a1010);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  padding:32px 24px 16px;min-height:320px;}
.fc-phone img{width:auto;max-width:100%;max-height:320px;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.8));}
.fc-body{padding:20px 24px 26px;}
.fc-tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(82,196,85,0.10);
  border:1px solid rgba(82,196,85,0.20);color:var(--gpale);
  font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:3px 11px;border-radius:50px;margin-bottom:11px;}
.fc-body h3{font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.35;}
.fc-body p{font-size:.84rem;color:var(--ts);line-height:1.65;}

/* FLOW */
.flow-sec{background:var(--d1);}
.flow-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:start;}
.flow-steps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:28px;margin-top:44px;}
.fstep{display:flex;gap:20px;}
.fnum{width:44px;height:44px;flex-shrink:0;border-radius:50%;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbrand),var(--gmid));
  color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:1rem;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  box-shadow:0 0 22px rgba(37,102,38,0.55);font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;}
.fstep h4{font-weight:700;font-size:.97rem;color:#fff;margin-bottom:6px;}
.fstep p{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--ts);line-height:1.68;}
.flow-screens{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;}
.flow-screen-wrap{border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;
  box-shadow:0 16px 56px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  background:#111;position:relative;}
.flow-screen-label{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  padding:8px 16px;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gpale);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;z-index:1;}
.flow-screen-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gglow);display:inline-block;}
.flow-screens img{width:100%;display:block;image-rendering:auto;}

/* DEPOIMENTOS */
.depo-sec{background:#000;}
.depo-intro{text-align:center;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 56px;}
.depo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;}
.dc{background:var(--d2);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.062);border-radius:20px;padding:30px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .25s,transform .25s;}
.dc:hover{border-color:rgba(82,196,85,0.22);transform:translateY(-5px);}
.dc::before{content:'"';position:absolute;top:-14px;right:18px;
  font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:7rem;color:var(--glight);opacity:.07;line-height:1;}
.stars{color:var(--gold);font-size:.88rem;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.depo-txt{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ts);line-height:1.74;margin-bottom:22px;font-style:italic;}
.depo-auth{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;}
.depo-av{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbrand),var(--gglow));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:1.1rem;}
.depo-name{font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;color:#fff;}
.depo-role{font-size:.73rem;color:var(--tm);margin-top:2px;}

/* CONTATO — simplificado, só diferencial + canais */
.contato-sec{background:var(--d1);}
.contato-inner{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;}
.contato-inner .h2{margin-bottom:18px;}
.contato-inner .body-txt{max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 48px;}
.contact-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto;}
.cc{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;padding:24px 28px;border-radius:18px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  transition:background .2s,border-color .2s,transform .2s;text-decoration:none;}
.cc:hover{background:rgba(82,196,85,0.09);border-color:rgba(82,196,85,0.28);transform:translateY(-4px);}
.cc-icon{width:54px;height:54px;flex-shrink:0;border-radius:15px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.55rem;}
.ci-wa{background:rgba(37,211,102,0.14);}
.ci-em{background:rgba(82,196,85,0.10);}
.cc-label{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tm);margin-bottom:5px;}
.cc-val{font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;color:#fff;}
.cc-sub{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--ts);margin-top:3px;}

/* PREÇO */
.preco-sec{background:#000;}
.preco-intro{text-align:center;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 56px;}
.preco-grid{display:flex;gap:22px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.pc{background:var(--d2);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);border-radius:26px;
  padding:44px 40px;min-width:284px;max-width:318px;position:relative;
  transition:border-color .25s,transform .25s;}
.pc:hover{border-color:rgba(82,196,85,0.3);transform:translateY(-7px);}
.pc.best{background:linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(37,102,38,0.25),rgba(25,72,25,0.3));
  border-color:rgba(82,196,85,0.38);transform:scale(1.05);}
.pc.best:hover{transform:scale(1.05) translateY(-7px);}
.best-tag{position:absolute;top:-15px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:var(--gold);color:#111;font-size:.67rem;font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 20px;border-radius:50px;white-space:nowrap;}
.pc-period{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.13em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--tm);margin-bottom:18px;}
.pc-price{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:3.6rem;color:#fff;line-height:1;}
.pc-price sup{font-size:1.3rem;vertical-align:top;margin-top:10px;display:inline-block;
  color:var(--ts);font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:400;}
.pc-price small{font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--tm);}
.pc-eco{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--gglow);font-weight:600;margin-top:8px;}
.pc-sep{border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);margin:26px 0;}
.pc-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:13px;margin-bottom:32px;}
.pc-list li{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:.86rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.74);line-height:1.5;}
.pc-list li::before{content:'✓';color:var(--gglow);font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.btn-ass{display:block;width:100%;text-align:center;background:var(--glight);color:#fff;
  font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;padding:15px;
  border-radius:12px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s,transform .15s;}
.btn-ass:hover{background:var(--gglow);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.pc.best .btn-ass{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbrand),var(--glight));
  box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(62,168,65,0.4);}

/* CTA */
.cta-sec{background:var(--d1);padding:120px 24px;text-align:center;}
.cta-box{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(20,56,20,0.9),rgba(28,70,28,0.85));
  border:1px solid rgba(82,196,85,0.18);border-radius:32px;padding:72px 52px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.cta-box::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% 0%,rgba(82,196,85,0.13),transparent);
  pointer-events:none;}
.cta-box h2{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,2.7rem);
  color:#fff;margin-bottom:18px;position:relative;}
.cta-box p{color:var(--ts);font-size:1.04rem;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 40px;
  position:relative;line-height:1.74;}
.cta-note{font-size:.77rem;color:var(--tm);margin-top:18px;position:relative;}

footer{background:#000;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;color:var(--tm);font-size:.78rem;}
footer img{height:40px;opacity:.6;margin:0 auto 16px;}
footer a{color:var(--gglow);}

/* BUY MODAL */
.buy-wrap{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.9);z-index:998;
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;}
.buy-wrap.open{display:flex;}
.buy-box{background:#0d0d0d;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);border-radius:24px;
  padding:46px 38px;max-width:430px;width:100%;text-align:center;position:relative;}
.buy-close{position:absolute;top:14px;right:18px;background:none;border:none;
  font-size:1.5rem;cursor:pointer;color:#444;}
.buy-box img{height:46px;margin:0 auto 20px;}
.buy-box h3{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.45rem;margin-bottom:8px;color:#fff;}
.buy-box p{color:#555;font-size:.86rem;margin-bottom:22px;}
.b-input{width:100%;padding:13px 16px;background:#161616;
  border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:10px;font-size:.93rem;
  margin-bottom:10px;outline:none;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;color:#fff;transition:border-color .2s;}
.b-input:focus{border-color:var(--gbrand);}
.b-input::placeholder{color:#444;}
.b-btn{width:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gbrand),var(--glight));
  color:#fff;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;
  padding:15px;border-radius:12px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .2s;}
.b-btn:hover{opacity:.88;}

/* REVEAL */
.rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);transition:opacity .75s ease,transform .75s ease;}
.rv.on{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.d1{transition-delay:.07s}.d2{transition-delay:.16s}.d3{transition-delay:.25s}.d4{transition-delay:.34s}

@media(max-width:960px){
  .dor-grid,.flow-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:44px}
  .feat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .depo-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .contact-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}
@media(max-width:640px){
  nav{padding:0 20px}.nav-link{display:none}
  .ph-side{display:none}.ph-center img{width:252px}
  .feat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .depo-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .preco-grid{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
  .pc.best{transform:none}
  .cta-box{padding:46px 26px}
  .sec{padding:80px 24px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="OAgroCota"></a>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <a href="#como-funciona" class="nav-link">Como funciona</a>
    <a href="#contato" class="nav-link">Contato</a>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="openBuy('anual')">Começar agora</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge"><span class="pdot"></span>Feito para consultores agrícolas</div>
  <h1>Você ainda perde horas<br>organizando cotação<br><em>no WhatsApp?</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Existe uma forma muito mais rápida — e profissional — de gerir cotações, comparar propostas e acompanhar a safra dos seus clientes. Tudo direto do celular.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <button class="btn-hero" onclick="openBuy('anual')">Quero conhecer o app →</button>
    <a href="#como-funciona" class="btn-ghost">Ver como funciona</a>
  </div>
  <div class="phones-hero">
    <div class="ph-side l"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Gestão financeira"></div>
    <div class="ph-center"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="App OAgroCota"></div>
    <div class="ph-side r"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Análise financeira"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 1. DOR -->
<section class="sec dor-sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="dor-grid">
      <div class="rv">
        <p class="label">A realidade do dia a dia</p>
        <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Reconhece alguma<br>dessas situações?</h2>
        <p class="body-txt" style="max-width:460px;">Quem trabalha como consultor agrícola domina a parte técnica. O que consome o tempo — e a energia — é toda a burocracia ao redor.</p>
        <div class="dor-cards">
          <div class="dor-card rv d1">
            <div class="dor-ico">📱</div>
            <div><h4>Cotação via WhatsApp e e-mail</h4>
            <p>Cada fornecedor recebe a lista num formato diferente, responde quando quer, e você junta tudo na mão. Um processo que se repete — e cansa — a cada safra.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="dor-card rv d2">
            <div class="dor-ico">📊</div>
            <div><h4>Uma planilha diferente por cliente</h4>
            <p>Calcular custo por hectare, ponto de nivelamento e margem de segurança para cada fazenda consome horas que deveriam estar em campo ou com novos clientes.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="dor-card rv d3">
            <div class="dor-ico">🔒</div>
            <div><h4>Fornecedor falando direto com o produtor</h4>
            <p>Sem um processo organizado, você perde o controle da negociação — e, em alguns casos, perde o próprio cliente junto.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Illustration replacing notification screenshot -->
      <div class="dor-visual rv d2">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Consultor sobrecarregado com planilhas e mensagens — situação que o OAgroCota resolve">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 2. COMO FUNCIONA -->
<section class="sec feat-sec" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="wrap">
